OL,5, Education, training and rehabilitation 
OL,6, needs to become the primary focus of   
OL,7, jails, the chief inspector of prisons  
OL,8, in England and Wales has said.         
OL,10,FCharlie Taylor told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,11,Fprogramme that a "fundamental          
OL,12,Freorientation" of the prison system was
OL,13,Fthe only way to reduce reoffending.    
OL,15,FHis intervention comes amid growing    
OL,16,Fconcern around overcrowding in jails.  
OL,18,FThe government says its new Prisoner   
OL,19,FEducation Service will improve outcomes
OL,20,Ffor those being released from custody. 
